# Redirect default Netlify subdomain to primary domain
http://stoplightio.netlify.com/*  http://stoplight.io/:splat 301!
https://stoplightio.netlify.com/* https://stoplight.io/:splat 301!

# External redirects
/login https://next.stoplight.io/login
/join https://next.stoplight.io
/register https://next.stoplight.io
/twitter https://twitter.com/stoplightio

# Internal redirects
/prism /mocking
/platform/prism /mocking
/platform/design /design
/platform/docs /documentation
/platform/scenarios /testing